ei.contract
Class ContractWrapper

java.lang.Object
  ei.contract.ContractWrapper

public class ContractWrapper
extends java.lang.Object

This class wraps an XML Contract and includes auxiliary methods for handling it. It also includes several methods for marshaling/unmarshaling the wrapped Contract object.

Author:
hlc
